parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shattering of the sunroof/moonroof can cause distraction, loss of concentration, and potentially lead to accidents or injuries.
Transmission problems can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
Brake problems can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
Locking system failures can cause inconvenience, safety risks, and potential theft.
Axle shaft assembly leaks can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
Electrical system failures can cause fires, accidents, and injuries.
Air conditioning problems can cause discomfort, distraction, and potential health risks.
symptoms: Intermittent or complete loss of air conditioning

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Shifter problems can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
Suspension and steering problems can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
Various other issues can cause inconvenience, safety risks, and potential accidents.
The poor performance of the headlights can cause reduced visibility, making it difficult to see pedestrians, animals, and road signs, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: have a dark area across the windshield
and do not illuminate the sides and upper part of the road.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the auto high beam system can cause the high beams to shut off unexpectedly, reducing visibility and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The auto high beam system shuts off
the green auto ready light does not come on
and the high beam light does not turn on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The tail light issues can cause reduced visibility, making it difficult for other drivers to see the vehicle, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: Water intrusion into the tail light
corrosion of the electronics and electrical connectors
and deterioration of the tail light lens.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The poor visibility of the reverse lights can cause accidents when reversing, especially in low-light conditions.
symptoms: The reverse lights are not visible to others
making it difficult to notice when the vehicle is reversing.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The dashboard lighting issues can cause distractions and reduce the driver's ability to see important information, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: requires excessive staring to determine quantities
and is affected by the angle of the sun.
